// CldSyncDisconnectRoot(a1,key,token,out): entry=lookup(key); if (*entry==token) disconnect; else 0xc000cf0b
// CldSyncDisconnectRootDeprecated(a1,key,out): entry=lookup(key); if (entry) disconnect;  // no token check

CldiPortInsertSyncRootNoLock (sub_1c005dd94 / unpatched sub_1c005ddb4), both binaries:
entry = CldiPortLookupSyncRootNoLock(a1, key0);
if (entry && *(entry+96) != 0 && *(entry+24) != token)
